node.text:
What race would @alex_bowman prefer to win? The #DAYTONA500 of course.

Get to know the No. 48 driver better before he climbs behind the wheel of the @allyracing Chevy @daytona!

node.title: This or That with Alex Bowman

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hendrick Motorsports on August 12, 2021 tagging @allyracing. May be an image of car, road and text that says 'BOWMA VMA 48 AHY INDIANAPOLIS ROAD COURSE SUNDAY, AUGUST 15 1 PMeT'.

node.text:
1️⃣ 4️⃣ left and right turns. 8️⃣ 2️⃣ laps. 2️⃣ 0️⃣ 0️⃣ miles of high-speed road course racing.

It's almost time to go #DoItRight at the @indianapolismotorspeedway road course!

Geared up to go battle for road course win No. 25. 🔥

Tune in to NBC on Sunday at 1 p.m. ET as our pilots take on the inaugural @indianapolismotorspeedway road course race!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hendrick Motorsports on August 12, 2021. May be an image of 4 people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text:
Before we take on the @indianapolismotorspeedway road course, let's throw it back to @jeffgordonweb's inaugural Brickyard 400 win in 1994! 

Who else remembers this historic win? #TBT

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Hendrick Motorsports on August 11, 2021 tagging @kylelarsonracin, and @valvoline. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text:
The last two times we took on new tracks (@nashvillesuperspeedway and @nascaratcota), our days ended in victory lane. 🏁

Tune in to NBC on Sunday at 1 p.m. ET as we take on the @indianapolismotorspeedway road course and look to make history at another new track!
